WEBVTT

00:01.849 --> 00:12.770
Now for puja, one has to understand that without
Realisation, puja has no meaning, because

00:12.770 --> 00:15.680
you are not ananya.

00:15.680 --> 00:26.610
Is, you have to become aware of your whole.

00:26.610 --> 00:30.340
Krishna’s description of Bhakti is ananya.

00:30.340 --> 00:42.780
He says, “I will give you ananya bhakti”,
He wants ananya bhakti, means when there is

00:42.780 --> 00:46.800
not the other, means when we are realised.

00:46.800 --> 00:54.370
Otherwise He says “Pushpam, phalam toyum”
(Bhagavad Gita verse 26) “A flower, a fruit

00:54.370 --> 01:04.600
and a water: whatever you give me I accept”
But when it comes to giving, He says, “You

01:04.600 --> 01:13.280
have to come to Me with ananya bhakti,”
means: when you have become

01:13.280 --> 01:21.210
one with Me, then you should have the devotion,
not before that.

01:21.210 --> 01:25.640
Before that, you are not connected.

01:25.640 --> 01:28.439
Now puja is the left hand side projection.

01:28.439 --> 01:35.250
It’s the neutralisation of the right side,
very much.

01:35.250 --> 01:41.020
Specially for people who are very right handed,
atmosphere which is very right handed, puja

01:41.020 --> 01:42.969
is ideal for them.

01:42.969 --> 01:51.840
Is the bhakti, is the devotion…that you
project.

01:51.840 --> 02:08.530
Now what happens actually when you project
this puja?

02:08.530 --> 02:12.800
It has been found out, and now as I am telling
you, that first you have to awaken within

02:12.800 --> 02:22.630
you the Deities that are still asleep, by
worshipping them.

02:22.630 --> 02:31.640
But as these Deities, Primordial Deities,
are with Me, you worship Me, and every Deity

02:31.640 --> 02:34.590
in Me is awakened, by which your Deities are
awakened.

02:34.590 --> 02:39.070
So first, your vibrations must improve, to
receive.

02:39.070 --> 02:49.290
If the reception is not good what’s the
use of any puja or projection?

02:49.290 --> 02:56.630
So first of all we, sort of, prepare our instrument,
or prepare our projecting instrument.

02:56.630 --> 03:07.010
That preparation is done by praying to different
Deities, as we call that: a Kundalini puja.

03:07.010 --> 03:13.390
By praying to My Kundalini you improve your
reflection.

03:13.390 --> 03:22.230
Because then the vibrations from Me start
flowing into yours and they awaken it.

03:22.230 --> 03:31.680
This is the projection as far as you are concerned.

03:31.680 --> 03:36.570
Once the instrument is alright, then you project
outside.

03:36.570 --> 03:42.500
And now how do you project?

03:42.500 --> 03:58.490
By worshipping the Goddess as the Protector
of the whole Universe, praising Her different

03:58.490 --> 04:08.850
attributes, even Her Face, Her Hands, everything
has a meaning.

04:08.850 --> 04:11.960
Praising Her Powers.

04:11.960 --> 04:22.500
By saying that, by repeating that, you echo
in your projection Her Powers, and then your

04:22.500 --> 04:24.540
projection becomes that powerful.

04:24.540 --> 04:33.290
It’s a very subtle happening that takes
place, it’s miraculous.

04:33.290 --> 04:40.850
These things look so simple, like just like
washing my Feet.

04:40.850 --> 04:42.100
Simple thing is washing my Feet.

04:42.100 --> 04:48.600
Now see these Feet, I don’t know if you
see, the whole Universe I see there and I

04:48.600 --> 04:52.530
really get stunned by them.

04:52.530 --> 04:57.140
When you wash My Feet, what do you do?

04:57.140 --> 05:02.490
Actually, My Feet have been working very hard.

05:02.490 --> 05:11.630
And then you put a little water to soothe
them, to suggest that you can feel the effort

05:11.630 --> 05:12.870
put in by these Feet.

05:12.870 --> 05:20.990
And a kind of a very sweet, melodious love
flows out of these Feet there.

05:20.990 --> 05:26.060
Like today I was coming, and I suddenly saw
Paul (Winter) standing.

05:26.060 --> 05:28.080
Same thing happened to me.

05:28.080 --> 05:35.110
See, what a care it is, what an understanding,
“Mother is coming, She should not be lost!”

05:35.110 --> 05:40.120
Just that, and the thing started melting.

05:40.120 --> 05:49.080
Because this love who understands everything,
doesn’t want anything, but is only excited

05:49.080 --> 05:51.960
if there is somebody to receive the love.

05:51.960 --> 05:54.620
Now how do you say you are going to receive?

05:54.620 --> 06:00.610
By expressing these small-small things.

06:00.610 --> 06:09.460
So when you soothe My Feet, wash Them, clean
Them, you know what They mean: you recognise.

06:09.460 --> 06:12.919
That recognition, how are you to show?

06:12.919 --> 06:17.889
You see, these ceremonies, little ceremonies
are important because they express your recognition.

06:17.889 --> 06:25.810
It could be absolutely dull, dead and finished,
and it could be absolutely living, if you

06:25.810 --> 06:29.120
know why you are doing it.

06:29.120 --> 06:37.560
Then you apply some oil and things [to] again
soothe My Feet.

06:37.560 --> 06:43.970
Just say, “Mother, You have worked very
hard, Your Feet have worked very hard."

06:43.970 --> 06:50.670
Just saying that itself, I mean makes no difference
otherwise, if you say in a very rational manner,

06:50.670 --> 06:56.840
but to that Love that are these Feet it makes
a very big difference.

06:56.840 --> 07:03.520
There is sweetness: a little thing, a little
baby just puts her hand on her mother’s

07:03.520 --> 07:11.949
cheeks, you see, just to express the gratitude,
and the mother’s heart starts jumping with

07:11.949 --> 07:12.949
love.

07:12.949 --> 07:23.790
It is a very reciprocal behaviour, it’s
very subtle and that kind of a subtle working

07:23.790 --> 07:33.270
is fixed already: it works that way only.

07:33.270 --> 07:35.930
The more you love from your heart, the more
the joy will be there.

07:35.930 --> 07:45.220
The more you are rational and more mental,
there won’t be so much joy.

07:45.220 --> 07:51.330
It should be [that] first of all your cleansing
is important but the projection should be

07:51.330 --> 07:58.240
towards your Mother, that is the height.

07:58.240 --> 08:10.130
Once you achieve that height, then you become
all-powerful, and then you can give to others.

08:10.130 --> 08:21.150
But that giving is nothing but is a very,
very, as I told you is a very mutual and absolutely

08:21.150 --> 08:22.150
reciprocal.

08:22.150 --> 08:25.830
Because the Devi knows about you, everything.

08:25.830 --> 08:32.460
If you are trying anything else, She knows
and She will also tell you frankly that this

08:32.460 --> 08:37.289
should not be done, that should not be done,
should not be done, clearly, so that you do

08:37.289 --> 08:40.579
not be under any misunderstandings about it.

08:40.579 --> 08:46.149
But still, to work it out, you must know it
has to be reciprocal, it cannot be one-sided.

08:46.149 --> 08:58.699
The sincerity cannot be one-sided, it has
to be both sides, then it works out better.

08:58.699 --> 09:10.850
And a kind of a homogeneous feeling with that
Love comes in, sort of a lubricant, a beautiful

09:10.850 --> 09:17.610
feeling of movement within yourself comes
in.

09:17.610 --> 09:23.009
Puja really is the triggering thing, it triggers
you.

09:23.009 --> 09:30.160
It triggers you into another realm, it’s
really miraculous.

09:30.160 --> 09:34.430
Once you have done the puja then you can project
out, much more, in your silence only.

09:34.430 --> 09:39.620
Your silence itself becomes so powerful.

09:39.620 --> 09:49.199
Now in this special case of our Western lives,
we have to established our innocence, very

09:49.199 --> 09:55.220
important, it is the first thing that is attacked,
innocence is attacked by so many things.

09:55.220 --> 09:59.269
So we have to established our innocence.

09:59.269 --> 10:04.740
And innocence is the most powerful thing:
it doesn’t see anything bad, it doesn’t

10:04.740 --> 10:10.069
see anything wrong, it doesn’t see anything…It
loves, just goes on loving, innocence.

10:10.069 --> 10:13.740
A child doesn’t know that the mother hates
the child.

10:13.740 --> 10:18.059
The child doesn’t know if anybody hates.

10:18.059 --> 10:19.819
In innocence they live.

10:19.819 --> 10:26.110
And then they suddenly discover sometimes,
they are shocked, how people are!

10:26.110 --> 10:30.920
They don’t love!

10:30.920 --> 10:35.730
They don’t love.

10:35.730 --> 10:37.570
So Ganesha is very important for the Western
countries, very important, because that’s

10:37.570 --> 10:46.110
the essence of everything, I think, that’s
the most essential thing.

10:46.110 --> 10:49.790
That’s why we worship Ganesha first.

10:49.790 --> 10:59.069
And Ganesha was created first of all, because
He is the eldest son, He’s the first son.

10:59.069 --> 11:15.310
He’s the eldest brother you have, and though
Kumara (Kartikeya) is treated as an elder

11:15.310 --> 11:24.589
brother always, while Ganesha calls Himself
as a younger brother, though He was the first

11:24.589 --> 11:27.279
created!

11:27.279 --> 11:29.839
Because He remains young always, never grows.

11:29.839 --> 11:35.420
So in a way, He’s always younger to you
also.

11:35.420 --> 11:42.319
It’s a very, very subtle understanding:
a very young little thing is so much wiser.

11:42.319 --> 11:43.319
He is wisdom.

11:43.319 --> 11:46.470
Can you imagine a little baby is so intelligent.

11:46.470 --> 11:49.350
A little baby so wise?

11:49.350 --> 12:01.410
Much more, He’s like a grown-up little baby,
a very matured, wise, little baby.

12:01.410 --> 12:13.639
So by age, you are always older than Him,
but by wisdom, He is the eldest.

12:13.639 --> 12:20.379
Then like this you should understand how we
evoke all the Deities within us by doing these

12:20.379 --> 12:23.279
small things, by saying Their mantras.

12:23.279 --> 12:28.589
Because now you are awakened, every word you
say is awakened now, is siddha mantra.

12:28.589 --> 12:37.519
On this Guru puja I’m really going to give
you the way of how to do the siddhartha is

12:37.519 --> 12:49.509
the establishment of the siddha.

12:49.509 --> 12:51.709
To master.

12:51.709 --> 12:57.079
To master every chakra and every deity bestowed
upon it.

12:57.079 --> 13:02.259
To master it, how to do it, I will tell you
this Guru puja no doubt.

13:02.259 --> 13:03.679
Going to work it out.

13:03.679 --> 13:15.189
But this puja is to be done with full understanding,
and with full recognition that it’s a great

13:15.189 --> 13:16.199
fortune.

13:16.199 --> 13:22.290
Even the Devas are jealous of you, all the
rishis are jealous of you, so many people

13:22.290 --> 13:24.250
are jealous of you.

13:24.250 --> 13:29.610
The greatest advantage for you, greatest fortune.

13:29.610 --> 13:34.029
Make full use of it.

13:34.029 --> 13:38.439
And they are very simple things that can please,
very simple.

13:38.439 --> 13:43.079
You know your Mother can be pleased with very,
very simple things.

13:43.079 --> 13:44.850
It’s like that only.

13:44.850 --> 13:51.610
It’s how much heart you have put into it,
is the point.

13:51.610 --> 13:55.689
I think tomorrow we should have the puja,
today we have understood about it.

13:55.689 --> 14:01.279
It is more to be felt and understood and realised
than to be thought about.

14:01.279 --> 14:03.689
Because you’ll go into thoughtless awareness.

14:03.689 --> 14:06.089
It is more source of triggering.

14:06.089 --> 14:12.509
For example, I think I’ll ask Hari (Jairam)
to give the miracle we had yesterday, would

14:12.509 --> 14:13.790
be [a] good idea.

14:13.790 --> 14:22.179
On our way we were coming, from…he was losing
his way throughout, and Regis (Camille) was

14:22.179 --> 14:28.059
navigating him (laughter) so we were all lost!

14:28.059 --> 14:34.980
But then we had a miracle while coming back:
there was in M1 (road) a complete jam and

14:34.980 --> 14:39.470
miles together we could see there is no movement.

14:39.470 --> 14:44.550
And suddenly, within two minutes, what happened,
what I told him, and how he worked it out.

14:44.550 --> 14:49.100
Hari has a problem you see, I think Felicity
(Payment) has the same mad problem.

14:49.100 --> 14:50.100
Where is she?

14:50.100 --> 14:51.100
Is she there?

14:51.100 --> 14:52.100
Yes?

14:52.100 --> 14:54.569
You see, like, to get after everything, to
do it…

14:54.569 --> 14:58.579
Now he thought that I have told that you put
your attention inside.

14:58.579 --> 15:06.850
Now he has a slope in his left side, as she
has too, and when you do it too much inside,

15:06.850 --> 15:08.529
you go on the slope.

15:08.529 --> 15:13.799
So Hari being a wiser person in this respect
because he’s not been a psychologist, he

15:13.799 --> 15:19.079
does not do that much, but Felicity does that,
is to go over do it.

15:19.079 --> 15:24.110
I mean she goes down very very deep into her
subconscious.

15:24.110 --> 15:27.320
While Hari understands there’s something’s
going wrong.

15:27.320 --> 15:30.769
I never said that you get after anything.

15:30.769 --> 15:35.859
Now, “put your attention inside” means:
if you get Realisation by that.

15:35.859 --> 15:39.689
If you don’t get Realisation, there’s
something wrong somewhere, you have lost your

15:39.689 --> 15:43.690
way, that’s the main point is.

15:43.690 --> 15:48.369
So I told Hari that, “You don’t put your
attention inside because you go on the slope,

15:48.369 --> 15:51.929
your car is such that it doesn’t go the
other way round, it goes into the slope, doesn’t

15:51.929 --> 15:54.819
go to the heart.

15:54.819 --> 16:00.730
So best thing is that now you [should] become
active outside and forget about it (the inside).

16:00.730 --> 16:03.279
And after some time you’ll receive a balance."

16:03.279 --> 16:05.079
I said “At this point.."

16:05.079 --> 16:08.279
Now he was trying to worry about the traffic.

16:08.279 --> 16:09.279
The other Mr.

16:09.279 --> 16:12.199
‘Navigator’ (Regis) was also busy worrying
about it!

16:12.199 --> 16:17.810
So I said, “Now, just now, you do not pay
any attention anywhere, you just project outside

16:17.810 --> 16:23.829
and think of everyone, how we are going to
get them realised” Only I said like this,

16:23.829 --> 16:24.829
and he started doing it.

16:24.829 --> 16:28.639
I said, “You never see the trees, you never
do this” And then what happened?

16:28.639 --> 16:29.639
You tell.

16:29.639 --> 16:30.639
Within 2 minutes time?

16:30.639 --> 16:34.170
Everybody, Chaya (Camille, Regis’ wife)
was there, all of them.

16:34.170 --> 16:37.709
Suddenly they found that the whole M1 (road)
was empty and they were rushing fast, you

16:37.709 --> 16:38.709
see.

16:38.709 --> 16:42.139
There was not, hardly one or two cars.

16:42.139 --> 16:45.319
The whole M1 was emptied, absolutely!

16:45.319 --> 16:49.500
And they did not know how it happened.

16:49.500 --> 16:50.850
Just they were there.

16:50.850 --> 16:53.339
And none of the things that we were going….

16:53.339 --> 16:57.109
Ray Harris: Was that yesterday afternoon on
the M1 Mother?

16:57.109 --> 16:59.239
Shri Mataji: Not today, yesterday

16:59.239 --> 17:00.239
Ray: Yesterday.

17:00.239 --> 17:05.010
Because I was on a coach there, and we were
in the traffic jam.

17:05.010 --> 17:11.139
Shri Mataji: Means you were in the traffic
jam! (laughter) The whole traffic jam

17:11.139 --> 17:16.779
Ray: We were 1 mile from the exit and it stopped
dead.

17:16.779 --> 17:22.720
And then we stayed there and suddenly it cleared
and there were no cars! (laughter)

17:22.720 --> 17:26.579
Shri Mataji: Suddenly the whole thing cleared
up!

17:26.579 --> 17:29.309
And suddenly, and they realised, and they
didn’t know how it cleared up.

17:29.309 --> 17:30.740
He speeded the car, I said “How?”

17:30.740 --> 17:35.960
He said, “The car, I don’t know” and
all the things that were in front of us, and

17:35.960 --> 17:38.340
all that, God knows where they disappeared
[to]!

17:38.340 --> 17:43.850
Such huge big things and on the sides and
this and that.

17:43.850 --> 17:44.980
Nothing!

17:44.980 --> 17:50.130
This is what is maya that upsets you.

17:50.130 --> 17:52.530
Project yourself outside.

17:52.530 --> 18:00.530
There was another experience I told these
people was this: that there were two journalists,

18:00.530 --> 18:01.530
one Mr.

18:01.530 --> 18:05.399
Marathe and a friend who are Sahaja Yogis,
and I went to the journalist’s association,

18:05.399 --> 18:06.880
they had a meeting.

18:06.880 --> 18:11.059
And there is another one who told Me, “No,
no Mother I have complete faith in You because

18:11.059 --> 18:15.070
there was a miracle that happened to a friend
of mine, Marathe, who is a Sahaja Yogi."

18:15.070 --> 18:16.200
I said, “What happened?”

18:16.200 --> 18:25.470
He said they were coming, by, from Poona down
to Bombay, and their brakes failed, and the

18:25.470 --> 18:29.350
slopes, you see, on the ghats (mountains),
it moves very fast.

18:29.350 --> 18:34.240
And suddenly they saw a huge big truck coming
up, with all the lights on top, and they didn’t

18:34.240 --> 18:36.159
know how to control, and they were about to
dash out.

18:36.159 --> 18:39.659
Just they closed their eyes and they said,
“Now, Mother, save us!”

18:39.659 --> 18:48.110
And suddenly they found that the car had crossed
the thing, and the thing was moving upwards,

18:48.110 --> 18:49.140
the truck was moving.

18:49.140 --> 18:56.600
They didn’t know, as if somebody had picked
up that car and put it on the other side.

18:56.600 --> 19:01.910
So these miracles can work out in case you
project yourself out.

19:01.910 --> 19:06.630
But for projecting outside, first you should
be cleansed inside.

19:06.630 --> 19:12.210
But for that also, all the time if your attention
[is like this -] “where am I catching?”

19:12.210 --> 19:13.720
Then you go onto rationality.

19:13.720 --> 19:18.929
“I must be catching because of this, I must
be catching because of that."

19:18.929 --> 19:24.850
I have told you hundred times not to say ‘why’.

19:24.850 --> 19:28.590
Give up this word ‘why’.

19:28.590 --> 19:31.580
“Why am I catching?”

19:31.580 --> 19:34.570
It will settle down.

19:34.570 --> 19:37.110
This maddening must go away!

19:37.110 --> 19:43.820
You cannot answer ‘why’ of anything in
Sahaja Yoga, can you?

19:43.820 --> 19:47.210
“Why did I meet you?”, “Why did you
get Realisation?”

19:47.210 --> 19:54.760
Ask hundred questions, two hundred, three
hundred, five hundred – you will not have

19:54.760 --> 19:55.760
any answer!

19:55.760 --> 19:57.350
So give up that.

19:57.350 --> 20:08.990
It’s not your rationality, it’s the Grace,
it’s the whim of the Grace that’s working

20:08.990 --> 20:11.760
it out!

20:11.760 --> 20:21.090
What are you trying at?

20:21.090 --> 20:23.950
Just ask for the Grace.

20:23.950 --> 20:24.950
Finished!

20:24.950 --> 20:25.950
It’s silent.

20:25.950 --> 20:26.950
It works out.

20:26.950 --> 20:27.950
This is maddening!

20:27.950 --> 20:28.950
You’ll become mad people.

20:28.950 --> 20:30.429
This is the greatest madness that people want
to know why of everything.

20:30.429 --> 20:31.960
How can you understand?

20:31.960 --> 20:36.380
You don’t have that chitti to understand
it.

20:36.380 --> 20:38.221
“[Mother] Can you explain?”

20:38.221 --> 20:39.221
How can I?

20:39.221 --> 20:43.400
If you make a little ant understand human
civilisation and this dirty politics you play

20:43.400 --> 20:44.400
it may understand.

20:44.400 --> 20:46.240
But you cannot understand ‘why’ of God.

20:46.240 --> 20:47.380
This is the relationship.

20:47.380 --> 20:53.960
So now, you give it up asking questions like
that.

20:53.960 --> 20:59.940
It’s too tremendous for this rationality.

20:59.940 --> 21:02.340
“Why God is doing?

21:02.340 --> 21:03.649
How He does?

21:03.649 --> 21:04.940
What are His powers?”

21:04.940 --> 21:10.519
Only thing [you can do] as scientists, you
note down – “Yes, it is so, yes, it is

21:10.519 --> 21:12.320
so, yes it is so."

21:12.320 --> 21:13.789
Verify it and note down.

21:13.789 --> 21:18.820
Only your awareness is changed from the scientist,
that you can see subtler working.

21:18.820 --> 21:20.110
But why it works?

21:20.110 --> 21:21.110
That’s His whim!

21:21.110 --> 21:22.110
He’ll do what He likes!

21:22.110 --> 21:25.940
Who are you to question God?

21:25.940 --> 21:28.260
How can you question God?

21:28.260 --> 21:37.410
Just give up asking this question ‘why’
and you will feel very much better.

21:37.410 --> 21:40.330
“It is God, you see, He does it!”

21:40.330 --> 21:41.640
This is what is faith.

21:41.640 --> 21:44.500
Not the blind, but real [faith], with understanding.

21:44.500 --> 21:50.509
I have told you this story of My grandmother
many a times, as she used to tell Me about

21:50.509 --> 21:55.919
faith, and which I have repeated to you so
many times, but again I’ll repeat it today:

21:55.919 --> 22:02.750
There were three people at different places,
and one man was going to see God.

22:02.750 --> 22:04.960
So they came to know about it.

22:04.960 --> 22:13.200
So one of them was in the forest, standing
on his head, doing all kinds of yogas and

22:13.200 --> 22:20.529
things like that, and praying to God – must
be with both hands towards Him, and soaking

22:20.529 --> 22:28.360
the feet, may be – like mad, you see, and
asking, “Why don’t You meet me?

22:28.360 --> 22:29.980
Why don’t You meet me?

22:29.980 --> 22:34.529
I want to meet You! why don’t you meet me?”

22:34.529 --> 22:39.000
And the man who was going to see God went
through that side, and He said, “Now please

22:39.000 --> 22:40.960
go and ask Him why don’t You come and see
me?

22:40.960 --> 22:43.519
You better come and see me, Why don’t You
do it?”

22:43.519 --> 22:50.299
So he said, “Alright, I’ll come, I’m
sorry” He had become thin, you see, absolutely

22:50.299 --> 22:52.720
thinned down, condition very miserable.

22:52.720 --> 22:59.700
He said, “Alright, I’ll go and tell God
about you."

22:59.700 --> 23:05.440
So, then he went up to God, no, no, before
that.

23:05.440 --> 23:14.909
Then he met another type who was sitting on
the street, and will be at the street side,

23:14.909 --> 23:15.909
and he said, “Oh!

23:15.909 --> 23:17.419
I heard you are going to meet God?”

23:17.419 --> 23:20.769
He said: yes, he is going to meet God.

23:20.769 --> 23:24.880
So he said, “Then communicate one small
little thing."

23:24.880 --> 23:27.940
He said, “What?”

23:27.940 --> 23:36.360
He said that, “Just tell Him I have had
no food, please send me my food now, I’m

23:36.360 --> 23:37.360
hungry."

23:37.360 --> 23:38.440
He said “What?”

23:38.440 --> 23:42.070
“Yes, you just tell Him that much."

23:42.070 --> 23:43.070
So he went up.

23:43.070 --> 23:44.070
He saw God.

23:44.070 --> 23:45.070
So God asked, “Did you meet some people
on your way?”

23:45.070 --> 23:47.570
He said, “Yes, I met a horrible one who
is all time saying ‘Why not?

23:47.570 --> 23:48.570
Why this?”

23:48.570 --> 23:50.789
And “Why?”, “Should I do it and should
I not?’

23:50.789 --> 23:54.149
And this and that, is going on.

23:54.149 --> 23:57.011
So, will You go and meet him?

23:57.011 --> 23:58.011
He’s asking."

23:58.011 --> 24:03.419
He (God) said, “No, better tell him to do
it little more, you see… still he has to

24:03.419 --> 24:04.419
do.

24:04.419 --> 24:05.419
He requires more effort.

24:05.419 --> 24:06.419
He won’t be satisfied.

24:06.419 --> 24:09.730
Till he gives up his efforts, let him go on."

24:09.730 --> 24:12.350
I mean he would have become mad like that.

24:12.350 --> 24:14.830
But now God says, “Alright, let him go ahead!

24:14.830 --> 24:15.830
What to do?

24:15.830 --> 24:16.830
If you tell them, they don’t want to listen,
so let them go ahead."

24:16.830 --> 24:23.200
Then he said, “Then I met another mad fellow,
who was on the street, he said that ‘ I’m

24:23.200 --> 24:25.410
hungry, ask God to send some food for me.

24:25.410 --> 24:26.410
Please ask.

24:26.410 --> 24:28.510
Tell God that I’m hungry.’

24:28.510 --> 24:29.510
” He (God) said, “Really?”

24:29.510 --> 24:30.510
He called all His managers He said, “Please
send his food.

24:30.510 --> 24:31.510
Have you not yet arranged his food and all
that?

24:31.510 --> 24:32.510
Please arrange it."

24:32.510 --> 24:34.100
He was quite surprised.

24:34.100 --> 24:36.160
He said, “What is this?

24:36.160 --> 24:41.730
This man is just telling ‘I’m hungry’,
and God is so much worried about this fellow

24:41.730 --> 24:45.549
and not worried about the fellow who is standing
on his head and asking such a lot of questions

24:45.549 --> 24:46.549
to God."

24:46.549 --> 24:53.330
So God knows everything, so He told him, “Now,
alright you are going down, you just tell

24:53.330 --> 24:57.490
them one story to both of them, and see their
reactions, and then you will know."

24:57.490 --> 24:59.330
So He told him a story.

24:59.330 --> 25:08.330
“You tell them that, ‘I went to God and
saw there, God passing a camel through the

25:08.330 --> 25:12.409
eye of a needle.’ ” and he said, “Really?”

25:12.409 --> 25:17.010
He said, “Yes, you go and tell them."

25:17.010 --> 25:18.750
So he came down.

25:18.750 --> 25:21.790
This fellow was still on his head.

25:21.790 --> 25:24.840
He came back, “What did God say?”

25:24.840 --> 25:28.360
He said you have to go on still for some time."

25:28.360 --> 25:29.360
He said, “Oh!

25:29.360 --> 25:30.360
Really?

25:30.360 --> 25:31.360
Well all glory to God!”

25:31.360 --> 25:32.380
He said, “Yes, he said so."

25:32.380 --> 25:33.380
He said, “Really?”

25:33.380 --> 25:35.149
Then, “Did you see something special there?”

25:35.149 --> 25:39.509
He said, “Yes, I saw that He passed a camel
through the eye of a needle!”

25:39.509 --> 25:43.299
He said, “No, no, don’t tell me stories!

25:43.299 --> 25:45.200
How can it?

25:45.200 --> 25:47.340
Such a big camel!

25:47.340 --> 25:48.890
How can it pass through the eye?

25:48.890 --> 25:50.559
After all it’s impossible!

25:50.559 --> 25:51.809
It is impossible!

25:51.809 --> 25:53.059
This is impossible!

25:53.059 --> 25:55.440
You are just now trying to befool me.

25:55.440 --> 25:58.470
Because you have been to God you think you
can befool me.

25:58.470 --> 26:02.200
No, no, I cannot take it, no, I cannot take
it!”

26:02.200 --> 26:06.539
So he went to another fellow, he was nicely
eating his food.

26:06.539 --> 26:07.620
He said, “Yes!

26:07.620 --> 26:11.980
I knew, you see, I just told you because you
asked me if you have to tell you anything,

26:11.980 --> 26:14.389
I knew God will send my food and everything.

26:14.389 --> 26:15.460
I’m quite alright."

26:15.460 --> 26:18.059
He said, “Did you see anything wondrous
there?”

26:18.059 --> 26:25.289
He said, “I saw the wonder of wonders, miracles
of miracles, that God passed a camel through

26:25.289 --> 26:28.570
the eye of a needle!”

26:28.570 --> 26:30.230
He said, “What is so miraculous?

26:30.230 --> 26:31.230
He is God!

26:31.230 --> 26:32.230
He’s God Almighty!

26:32.230 --> 26:33.230
What?

26:33.230 --> 26:35.929
He can pass even Universes after Universes
through that hole!

26:35.929 --> 26:37.970
What is it for God?

26:37.970 --> 26:39.799
He is God Almighty don’t you understand
God Almighty?

26:39.799 --> 26:42.200
Because you have met Him, you think He’s
nothing!

26:42.200 --> 26:47.640
Because you did it so easily, you think He’s
nothing!

26:47.640 --> 26:50.509
Because He behaves like [that] you think He’s
nothing!

26:50.509 --> 26:52.240
He’s God Almighty!

26:52.240 --> 26:53.409
So what?

26:53.409 --> 26:55.700
to Him, what is it?”

26:55.700 --> 27:01.509
Then
he realised.

27:01.509 --> 27:02.509
This is Faith.

27:02.509 --> 27:05.799
That is what is enlightened within you with
puja.

27:05.799 --> 27:10.100
Not your rationality which is brought down
actually quite a lot.

27:10.100 --> 27:16.840
So with this idea, tomorrow, we’ll have
the puja, alright?

27:16.840 --> 27:21.330
May God Bless You.

27:21.330 --> 27:31.440
Sahaja Yogi: Jane just started labour, for
the baby.

27:31.440 --> 27:35.929
Shri Mataji: Has started?

27:35.929 --> 27:39.299
Good, good, good.

27:39.299 --> 27:43.789
It will work out.

27:43.789 --> 27:51.529
In Jane’s case she never wanted a baby – big
problem, you see.

27:51.529 --> 27:57.720
Funny ideas about children are developing
in this horrible country, which is so shocking,

27:57.720 --> 27:59.279
so shocking.

27:59.279 --> 28:06.249
I mean the mother is the one who should have
feelings.

28:06.249 --> 28:10.509
Every day you read such horrible stories about
these mother’s.

28:10.509 --> 28:11.730
Can’t imagine!

28:11.730 --> 28:18.830
They can be so cruel?

28:18.830 --> 28:23.750
The more I read about these things, one can’t
understand.

28:23.750 --> 28:25.690
How can they be cruel?

28:25.690 --> 28:33.679
I mean if you hear a little thorn has gone
into the feet of a child your heart starts

28:33.679 --> 28:38.990
melting, you know.

28:38.990 --> 28:44.309
Innocence, is attack on innocence.

28:44.309 --> 28:48.179
The whole country is after innocence.

28:48.179 --> 28:55.549
Is old men running after young girls, all
this is attack on innocence.

28:55.549 --> 29:03.000
I mean, extremely satanic, very satanic forces
are let loose.

29:03.000 --> 29:15.250
They are attacking all the children of the
world and everything.

29:15.250 --> 29:16.250
Yogini: Would You like some tea, Mother?

29:16.250 --> 29:17.250
Would you like some tea?

29:17.250 --> 29:20.110
Shri Mataji: No, but I think we’ll have
food.

29:20.110 --> 29:21.200
Better to have food.

29:21.200 --> 29:25.120
I’ve got some food for you.

29:25.120 --> 29:36.210
Heat it up and I hope you’ll like it.

29:36.210 --> 29:39.179
Now.

29:39.179 --> 29:43.809
Got something for her.

29:43.809 --> 30:03.820
Can you imagine where people are killing their
wives, their husbands?

30:03.820 --> 30:08.549
Yesterday, today, My husband was telling Me
there was a case where a wife was killed and

30:08.549 --> 30:11.539
was put in the fridge, deep freeze.

30:11.539 --> 30:14.139
Can you imagine?

30:14.139 --> 30:18.789
And then Peter (Pierce) told another story
that a lady delivered her child in the loo

30:18.789 --> 30:20.509
and left the child [to] die there.

30:20.509 --> 30:22.840
I mean, this kind of people can you imagine?

30:22.840 --> 30:26.519
They have only sex-love and a sort of dirty
feelings for others, they have never good,

30:26.519 --> 30:29.039
pure feelings for anyone else.

30:29.039 --> 30:32.570
What should you say to such people?

30:32.570 --> 30:34.590
I just can’t understand.

30:34.590 --> 30:35.600
Very destructive.

30:35.600 --> 30:36.600
Satanic.

30:36.600 --> 30:41.480
You see but there must be something satanic
in people to accept such satanic things.

30:41.480 --> 30:47.659
I mean I cannot think of one case in India
– one case – where a mother could kill

30:47.659 --> 30:48.659
the child.

30:48.659 --> 30:50.149
One case I cannot think.

30:50.149 --> 30:54.960
Even if it’s a illegitimate child she would
not like to kill but others may like to finish

30:54.960 --> 30:56.549
it off.

30:56.549 --> 31:01.320
That’s different, but she would not.

31:01.320 --> 31:08.470
I mean just can’t think of such a thing.

31:08.470 --> 31:09.470
Unbelievable!

31:09.470 --> 31:10.470
Unbelievable.

31:10.470 --> 31:14.830
They are so egoistical, so foolish.

31:14.830 --> 31:15.830
Donkeys they could be only.

31:15.830 --> 31:20.759
At the most donkeys are like that, I think,
that’s why Christ rode on the donkeys.

31:20.759 --> 31:24.110
Donkeys, are they egoistical?

31:24.110 --> 31:29.970
I don’t think so, they are not.

31:29.970 --> 31:35.480
Moreover they are not also full of hatred,
donkeys are not full of hatred.

31:35.480 --> 31:38.840
They are stupid people.

31:38.840 --> 31:42.409
You see, somebody must bully them then they
are alright.

31:42.409 --> 31:49.330
The bullying starts like this: a French bullies
English, I have seen it, puts them down.

31:49.330 --> 31:55.340
French think they are higher than the [English].

31:55.340 --> 31:58.009
See the gradation is in the opposite direction.

31:58.009 --> 32:01.740
They think that the English are lower; I think
definitely English are better than French

32:01.740 --> 32:10.889
as far as evolution is concerned, but the
French have put them down.

32:10.889 --> 32:14.159
Yesterday I met – there was one Bangladeshi
who was going back to Bangladesh.

32:14.159 --> 32:15.730
He says, “Many have gone from here.

32:15.730 --> 32:19.899
People don’t know how many have gone; if
they write it down they’ll be amazed, because

32:19.899 --> 32:20.899
they are fed up."

32:20.899 --> 32:24.740
And funny, funny things, you see he told Me,
he lived with four types of neighbours and

32:24.740 --> 32:26.900
he got so fed up with them.

32:26.900 --> 32:32.860
First neighbour he lived with, you see, he
said that, “He had a daughter and I had

32:32.860 --> 32:35.809
a daughter of the same age, 14 years of age.

32:35.809 --> 32:37.369
And he [the Englishman] said ‘Why shouldn’t
we exchange our daughters, you see, for lovemaking?’

32:37.369 --> 32:41.269
“ He got so angry and he ran away.

32:41.269 --> 32:44.190
Shri Mataji laughing: How can he?

32:44.190 --> 32:46.940
This was the first thing.

32:46.940 --> 32:52.490
Then the second one was, he said that, You
see, his daughter was – little nausea she

32:52.490 --> 32:53.559
had or something.

32:53.559 --> 32:55.340
She’s just 14 or something.

32:55.340 --> 33:00.039
So she went to the doctor and doctor said,
“Did you – have you start giving her [contraceptive]

33:00.039 --> 33:01.309
pills and things, you see?”

33:01.309 --> 33:03.330
This upset him absolutely then.

33:03.330 --> 33:07.919
Like that he gave Me four horrible instances,
the two others I cannot tell you to what extent

33:07.919 --> 33:08.919
it is.

33:08.919 --> 33:11.909
He said, “I’m not going to live in this
country."

33:11.909 --> 33:18.730
I mean, they are just like stud-bulls going
round, I tell you – horrible.

33:18.730 --> 33:20.190
And the women I don’t know what to call
them!

33:20.190 --> 33:21.190
What is the parallel?

33:21.190 --> 33:22.309
(laughing) Hawkers?

33:22.309 --> 33:23.509
Or what?

33:23.509 --> 33:24.710
The Hawks?

33:24.710 --> 33:28.499
What do you call the other side?

33:28.499 --> 33:29.639
Yogini: Hookers.

33:29.639 --> 33:31.340
Shri Mataji: Hooker?

33:31.340 --> 33:32.340
Hookers.

33:32.340 --> 33:35.320
Yogini: They get paid for it.

33:35.320 --> 33:37.029
Shri Mataji: Ha?

33:37.029 --> 33:38.389
Yogini: They get paid for it.

33:38.389 --> 33:39.389
Shri Mataji: They get paid for.

33:39.389 --> 33:40.389
Yes they get paid for.

33:40.389 --> 33:49.690
Shri Mataji: At least they can have a date
and have some nice food somewhere in the Chinese.

33:49.690 --> 33:51.000
(laughing).

33:51.000 --> 33:59.730
Selling their chastity for cheap things.

33:59.730 --> 34:01.140
Different community altogether.

34:01.140 --> 34:05.990
It’s a very nice picture, eh?

34:05.990 --> 34:20.640
There’s only a Radha and Krishna both together
in One Being.

34:20.640 --> 34:23.160
You have got of My eyes in many of My photographs.

34:23.160 --> 34:26.929
Some of these are.What is this one about?

34:26.929 --> 34:28.210
Really terrible.

34:28.210 --> 34:30.140
Ramadan, you see.

34:30.140 --> 34:35.270
Yesterday I must tell you, where is he?

34:35.270 --> 34:37.200
(Djamel) Yesterday Ramadan.

34:37.200 --> 34:44.850
Yesterday these Muslims came in, you see,
they were waiting for 8 [O’clock], something

34:44.850 --> 34:46.430
time, you see?

34:46.430 --> 34:48.410
And then they started drinking like hell,
I mean they drank so much of (laughter).

34:48.410 --> 34:50.060
By the way why did they do it?

34:50.060 --> 34:52.960
In the daytime what happened?

34:52.960 --> 34:54.740
What is the story?

34:54.740 --> 34:59.080
Djamel Metouri: Why do they do it?

34:59.080 --> 35:02.920
What do they do during the daytime?

35:02.920 --> 35:09.893
Shri Mataji: No-no-no-no no, no, why – what
is the story, why did they fast?

35:09.893 --> 35:10.893
Djamel: Well it’s for the Koran, the Prophet
Mohammed decided that every year there should

35:10.893 --> 35:11.893
be a time when all the people should fast
to keep all their ?

35:11.893 --> 35:12.893
at bay.

35:12.893 --> 35:18.690
Akbar: To keep all the attentions at bay.

35:18.690 --> 35:20.550
Shri Mataji: They should fast – what…?

35:20.550 --> 35:25.280
Yogi: They should fast for one month because
they have for at least one month in a year

35:25.280 --> 35:32.160
to keep away, You know, temptation from drinking
and…

35:32.160 --> 35:39.720
Because at the time they were very licentious,
You know they used to –

35:39.720 --> 35:45.120
Shri Mataji: Dining and wining!

35:45.120 --> 35:55.540
Djamel: Well they do still, but at the time
they were much more.

35:55.540 --> 35:59.550
Shri Mataji: They used to drink like anything.

35:59.550 --> 36:02.960
So He said, “You better fast for one month,
because He thought if you put one month, at

36:02.960 --> 36:03.960
least for one day they will do it.

36:03.960 --> 36:04.960
(Laughter)

36:04.960 --> 36:06.700
You see this is how, you have to put an extreme
case, you see?

36:06.700 --> 36:11.030
But people say that, “Why they put an extreme
case?”

36:11.030 --> 36:16.250
Because, you see if you put an extreme case
then at least symbolically you’ll do for

36:16.250 --> 36:17.560
one day or half a day.

36:17.560 --> 36:22.350
That was the reason, you see, because they
never believed in fasting.

36:22.350 --> 36:26.130
They used to eat, gluttonous people, you see,
horrible!

36:26.130 --> 36:32.930
They were living in tribes and very much eating,
all the time attention was on eating.

36:32.930 --> 36:34.920
Djamel: It was not just that, You see all
men should not eat salt anywhere, You know

36:34.920 --> 36:36.280
I mean –

36:36.280 --> 36:43.320
Shri Mataji: That all will start there.

36:43.320 --> 36:47.660
Djamel: And you mustn’t listen to anything
harsh from people

36:47.660 --> 36:50.430
Shri Mataji: This was only for His disciples.

36:50.430 --> 36:53.890
Djamel: He was trying too, Mother, and to
look at –

36:53.890 --> 36:55.620
Shri Mataji: -women – adulterous eyes.

36:55.620 --> 36:56.620
That they all do!

36:56.620 --> 36:59.250
You see, at least He must have thought that,
“Give one month a trial, the whole year

36:59.250 --> 37:00.250
you can’t do.

37:00.250 --> 37:05.740
So, one month give a trial like that,” you
see so He said, “Alright, try for one month."

37:05.740 --> 37:13.400
(laughing) But they can do fasting, is alright,
and then when did he say that, eat in the

37:13.400 --> 37:19.480
morning and eat in the evening?

37:19.480 --> 37:24.140
Djamel: Yes, it’s said that you must fast
from dark to –

37:24.140 --> 37:26.720
Other yogi: Dawn to Dusk.

37:26.720 --> 37:28.180
Djamel: Moonrise, I mean.

37:28.180 --> 37:31.450
Shri Mataji: But they eat with vengeance at
both the times!

37:31.450 --> 37:34.850
Djamel: But they do in the night, they eat…

37:34.850 --> 37:38.390
Shri Mataji: …with vengeance, you see, so
everything is put upside down., Why He said

37:38.390 --> 37:40.990
it because, you see, all these systems were
for his disciples.

37:40.990 --> 37:45.610
They would do Namaz for five times, He thought
that He might be able to achieve the Realization

37:45.610 --> 37:46.970
part of it, you see.

37:46.970 --> 37:51.610
So He said, “All right, for one month, let’s
have a course like that."

37:51.610 --> 37:56.060
See they went on a course, sort of thing,
“Let’s work it out."

37:56.060 --> 37:58.910
And that thing has become a pattern now that
they fast.

37:58.910 --> 38:02.460
It’s all nonsense, it’s madness.

38:02.460 --> 38:12.240
Djamel: Mother I think it must be very good,
if someone is going to meditate, You know,

38:12.240 --> 38:15.410
but for one whole month it’s a lot.

38:15.410 --> 38:27.290
Shri Mataji: See, if they are paying attention
to their food only, waiting for the time to

38:27.290 --> 38:31.300
come to drink it’s nonsense!

38:31.300 --> 38:34.460
Djamel: That’s what they do.

38:34.460 --> 38:37.840
Djamel: But people go extreme You see even
when they’re weak person.

38:37.840 --> 38:39.970
A person should be able to stand it.

38:39.970 --> 38:41.100
But they still do it.

38:41.100 --> 38:44.080
And they end up in hospitals and when they
die they’re considered as martyrs.

38:44.080 --> 38:45.080
Shri Mataji: What do they say?

38:45.080 --> 38:47.160
Djamel: You know it’s supposed to be very
good to die in Ramadan.

38:47.160 --> 38:48.160
(laughter)

38:48.160 --> 38:49.160
Shri Mataji: Imagine.

38:49.160 --> 38:52.170
Djamel: And if there is a war you must be
right in front line.

38:52.170 --> 38:56.540
Shri Mataji: Yes, like in the war you are
dying.

38:56.540 --> 39:01.650
That’s a war in a way, because you war against
your weaknesses, war against your habits and

39:01.650 --> 39:03.120
things, it’s true, no doubt!

39:03.120 --> 39:09.330
But that is a regular stuff, which one has
to do, but that’s not done, it’s something

39:09.330 --> 39:10.330
very different, you know.

39:10.330 --> 39:13.730
Djamel: Crazy people live today, You know.

